_text = "Over the years, this space changed a lot. Every month or so I would come up with some cool new floor plan that would outdo the old one.\n\nI was always creating messes then spending entire days rearranging the mess to make some sort of new layout.\n\nEvery september, my dad would reclaim the space to begin decorating for halloween. To this day, he loves building and creating. I strongly believe I became an artist because of his influence. He doesn't call himself an artist, but I believe he is.\n\nHe would spend months designing these sculptures that would fit specific halloween themes."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, BasementHalloweenMemory, BasementHalloweenMemory, false)
